en="1921-12-28" n="01">28. 12. 1921</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb10992">Brandes, Georg</persName><placeName ref="#pmb36300">Kopenhagen</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10992">Brandes, Georg</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02371">Schnitzler an Bahr, 16. 12. 1921</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02373">Brandes an Schnitzler, 5. 1. 1922</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02355">Schnitzler an Brandes, 21. 8. 1920</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02373">Brandes an Schnitzler, 5. 1. 1922</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
